Name: Very strange old man killed his wife!!
Genre: Criminal
Main_Text: A 91-year-old man has been charged with the murder of his 92-year-old wife. Police are investigating John Woodbridge after Anne Woodbridge was found dead at a home in Weston-super-Mare on Monday morning. After appearing before Bristol Magistrates Court today he is now due to appear at Bristol Crown Court on March 17. In a statement, Avon and Somerset Police said: A man has been charged after an investigation into the death of a woman in Weston-super-Mare. Anne Woodbridge, 92, was found deceased at a residential address on the morning of Monday 30 January. John Woodbridge, of Ashcombe Road, has subsequently been charged with murder.
Author: Vladislav Kuziakin
Date: 3 4 2023